{
  "texts": [
    "The selection of strong treatments started with the BBBC022 and BBBC036 datasets (chemical perturbations).",
    "We selected the 500 strongest treatments (see Measuring treatment effect) from BBBC022 and searched for those in BBBC036, which resulted in 301 strong treatments in common between both datasets.",
    "We additionally selected 50 unique treatments from BBBC022 and 62 unique treatments from BBBC036.",
    "Out of those 413 treatments, 122 overlapped with the LINCS dataset and were included.",
    "We additionally selected 7 random treatments from LINCS, from top 20 (by number of associated treatments) MoAs."
  ]
}